Purple Agrees to Buy South African Sports Betting Company For $8.7 Million

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-31T10:36:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/purple-agrees-to-buy-south-african-sports-betting-company-for-8-7-million.html
Purple Capital Ltd. (PPE)  said it has
entered into an agreement to buy a “significant player in the
sports betting industry” in  South Africa  for 60 million rand.  The transaction is still subject to conditions, Purple
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
